headline.main: Deutsche Boerse Blames Britain for Failed LSE Tie-Up: Chairman in Paper
headline.print_headline: Deutsche Boerse Blames Britain for Failed LSE Tie-Up: Chairman in Paper

lead_paragraph: Deutsche Boerse Chairman Joachim Faber has put the blame for a failed tie-up with the London Stock Exchange on Britain and its vote to leave the European Union.
